parameters: Was there no problem...? That's good.

Again... I didn't particularly feel any magic
being activated, but...

We were supposed to move together... Why is it
only Amelia?
(Is she already involved in some kind of problem?)

(If that's the case... why didn't she consult with
me...)

(No, I feel the same... Everyone has things they
can't say)

(The question is whether Hoffman is involved or
not)
(I have a bad feeling about this...)

Don't make such a serious face. Sending errors
with teleportation stones are rare.

Especially the ones inside the academy are old, so
sometimes they get sent to a different location.

Is that so... I didn't know because I don't use
teleportation stones very often.

Because they are only placed in large cities or
big facilities.
Well, there's no need to worry that much.

For now, I'll wait here. Amelia came here last
time too.
In that case, I'll stay too.
I have something I want to talk about.
